net.wequick.small

Class ApkBundleLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.wequick.small.BundleLauncher
      • net.wequick.small.SoBundleLauncher
        • net.wequick.small.ApkBundleLauncher

  • public class ApkBundleLauncher
extends SoBundleLauncher
    This class launch the plugin activity by it's class name.

    This class resolve the bundle who's pkg is specified as "*.app.*" or *.lib.* in bundle.json.

    The *.app.* plugin contains some activities, While launching, this class takes the bundle's uri as a shortcut of the plugin launcher activity class name. the other activities can be specified by the bundle's rules.

    The *.lib.* plugin usually consists exclusively of global methods that operate on your product services.

    See Also:
    ActivityLauncher
